trans-unit.source: Provides functionality to create new classes from values in a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinqDataSource" /> control.
trans-unit.target: 提供可通过 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinqDataSource" /> 控件中的值创建新类的功能。

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinqDataSource.Select%2A> property is set to an expression that contains the `new` function, a class is dynamically created that contains only the properties specified in the `new` function.
trans-unit.target: 当<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinqDataSource.Select%2A>属性设置为包含的表达式`new`函数，动态创建类，其中包含仅中指定的属性`new`函数。

trans-unit.source: The parser creates the `new` class by extending the <xref:System.Web.Query.Dynamic.DynamicClass> class.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Query.Dynamic.DynamicClass" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.Query.Dynamic.DynamicClass" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: Returns a string representation of the dynamic class.
trans-unit.target: 返回动态类的字符串表示形式。

trans-unit.source: A string that represents the dynamic class and its properties.
trans-unit.target: 一个表示动态类及其属性的字符串。

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinqDataSource.Select%2A> property is set to an expression that contains the `new` function, a class is dynamically created that contains only the properties specified in the `new` function.
trans-unit.target: 当<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinqDataSource.Select%2A>属性设置为包含的表达式`new`函数，动态创建类，其中包含仅中指定的属性`new`函数。

trans-unit.source: The parser creates the `new` class by extending the <xref:System.Web.Query.Dynamic.DynamicClass> class.
The <xref:System.Web.Query.Dynamic.DynamicClass.ToString%2A> methods creates a string representation of the properties in the class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Query.Dynamic.DynamicClass.ToString%2A>方法在类中创建的字符串表示形式的属性。
